trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of static <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> objects, which is used when the connections are declared in content pages and the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control is declared in a master page.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en samling av statiske <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> objekter, som brukes når tilkoblinger er deklarert i innhold sider og <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> kontrollen er deklarert i en hoveddokumentet.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection class is used in a specific development scenario.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection brukes i et bestemt utviklingsscenario.

trans-unit.source: If a Web Parts application uses master pages, with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control declared in a master page, and individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> objects declared in content pages as static connections, the ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection class is used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en webdeler-programmet bruker master sider, med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollerer deklarert i en hoveddokumentet og individuelle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>objekter deklarert i innhold sider som statisk tilkoblinger ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection klassen brukes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: In the content pages, multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> controls can be declared, which differs from the ordinary rule that only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control can be declared on a page.
trans-unit.target: I innhold sidene flere <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>Kontroller kan deklareres, som er forskjellig fra den vanlige regelen at bare én <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen kan deklareres på en side.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control on a content page can contain a `<StaticConnections>` element, and this element can contain one or more declared `<asp:webpartconnection>` elements.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontrollen i et kan inneholde en `<StaticConnections>` elementet, og dette elementet kan inneholde én eller flere deklarert `<asp:webpartconnection>` elementer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection class is used by the Web Parts control set to create a collection of all the static connections declared in each content page, and these collections are ultimately added to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> collection in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection brukes av webdeler kontrollen for å opprette en samling av alle de statiske tilkoblingene som er deklarert i hver innhold side, og disse samlingene til slutt er lagt til i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>samlingen i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection class is used to create the collection of static <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> objects that is referenced by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection brukes til å opprette samlingen av statiske <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>objekter som refererer til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>
